   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``I can't tell you how many times I've walked into a store or
mall and heard my dad singing. I just get this really nice feeling,
as if he's saying, `Hey, how are you?' or `I'm still around.' It's
almost magical.''
</P>
