   &UR; SEE YOU LATER &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``Stop thinking that everyone else is living in a  &UR; Norman &LR; 
 &UR; Rockwell  &LR; painting,'' says  &UR; Diane de Castro &LR; , author of
``Connecting in San Francisco.'' You can connect to a new family
for the holidays ``through friendship.''
</P>
<P>
   And  &UR; Wally Meerschaert &LR;  cites highway signs that provide perfect
advice for the New Year: ``Keep Clear.''
</P>
<P>
   See you in January.
