MRFOX-STAGE (Los Angeles) _ If cats can be stars of a Broadway
show, don't foxes at least deserve their own opera? To judge by
L.A. Opera's ``Fantastic Mr. Fox,'' now playing at the Dorothy
Chandler Pavilion, foxes certainly can sing and emote every bit as
well as their feline counterparts. By Reed Johnson. 
. 
