long, personal battle to remove President Clinton from office.
Barr, one of the most conservative members in the House, started
his campaign well before the Lewinsky issue emerged. By MARK HELM.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-MIDEAST (Washington) _ Facing an impeachment vote in the
