   FBC-GSOUTHERN _ Georgia Southern looks to move one step closer
to the Division I-AA championship game today when it hosts Western
Illinois in the semifinals in Statesboro. With a victory, Georgia
Southern would advance to the finals for the first time since 1990.
(Reese, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
