<P>
   FBN-RIVALS _ The Atlanta-New Orleans rivalry used to be one of
the most interesting in the NFL, because both were so inept that
strange things tended to happen when the two played. We relive the
lowlights through the eyes of those who participated. (Pasquarelli,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-FEATURE _ Feature to be named. (Pasquarelli, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
