   IMPEACH (Washington) _ After a passionate debate that was at
turns grave, partisan and even sorrowful, the House Judiciary
Committee is expected to vote along party lines Friday to impeach
President Clinton and remove him from office. By Alison Mitchell.
</P>
<P>
   With photo and graphic.
</P>
