<P>
   Mr. Gorsky had finally died and so Neil Armstrong felt he could
answer the question. When he was a kid, he was playing baseball
with a friend in the backyard. His friend hit a ball, which landed
in the front of his neighbor's bedroom windows. His neighbor's were
Mr. and Mrs. Gorsky. As he leaned down to pick up the ball, young
Armstrong heard Mrs. Gorsky shouting at Mr. Gorsky. `Oral sex! You
want oral sex?! You'll get oral sex when the kid next door walks on
the moon!`
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
